  "body": "The current implementation of the Channel avatar component is missing two pieces in the design spec.\r\n\r\n1- The icon size might change, as such it is better to have a bounding box of 20px around the emoji so that the spacing etc is consistent but allows for emojis of different sizes to be used. \r\n\r\n2 - The lock/unlock icon should have an option to use a mask so that it shows the color below the channel avatar component.\r\n\r\nreach out to design team if there is some confusion in what's needed.\r\n\r\nAcceptance criteria. \r\n- Implement 1 & 2.\r\n- get the green light from the design team.\r\n- Adjust channel list component to use the mask feature for the lock/unlock icon.\r\n\r\n",
